      -> {"CONFIRMED" if test1_different else "REJECTED"}: SGD and Muon spectra are {'significantly' if test1_different else 'NOT significantly'} different

  T2: WASSERSTEIN DISTANCE IS NON-TRIVIAL
      Mean Wasserstein distance (normalized spectra): {mean_wd:.6f}  (threshold: 0.001)
